{"type": "article", "id": 13158, "title": "五颜六色的木材", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-07T07:28:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104233cNzPIGn8V367MWae.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自德国的设计师 Meike Harde 通过给木材表面上色，制成了五彩缤纷的木板，并打造了一系列浪漫的家具，包括屏风，边桌，茶几等。她的方法是把各色颜料倒在木材表面，让它们自由蔓延，交融，等颜料完全干后，在木材表面刷一层透明漆，最终做成这些五颜六色的木板，由此也启发人们自由给木材上色，让家具变得更加缤纷有趣。这是<a href=\"http://meikeharde.com/\" target=\"_blank\">她的个人主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140754Yt0BfyriuAacvVo9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140754FUrGJENIVO1d3nbg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140755bkTNV2oGsjFPxfC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74270833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140755CG1MVmscik3Op2eQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140756FDiQ0lJ9hWsBxoAt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407561BGpw5tE34r827kH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407579EhAJ5jcSXk0oHTO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614075739i6FCt4XjHWaQTo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614075846mi01HL82Ql7aJ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140758bHlDz9A6kpKo4Mwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140759mPkl2vyxRBcZK0nC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}